S wakka i gxedmen igellil n lebḥeṛ ur yefnu ara, ma d aẓekkun-agi ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ.
Di temdint n Jafa, ameqqran n tejmaɛt i d-yețwaɛfan n temdint n Lquds, wwin-t tiseḍwa amezwaru n temdint n Lquds. Ițțumetlen ayen uran yismawen n temdint n Kurintus daɣen iwumi qqaṛen iguṣari.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Ma yella ayen yesɛan azal, ilaq aț-țemfaṛaqem ɣer wayen yesɛan azal d ameqqran.
Meɛna m'ara d-uɣalen si s ɣuṛ-es lewqam, ad jemɛen wid yelhan, ad ḍeggṛen wid n lexla ur keččmen ara ɣer deffir-nsen.
Ițmeslay-asen-d akka iwakken ad țeklen iman-nsen. Ayen akken i t-isselmed seg wedrum n Zakarya di tmurt n Maṣeṛ, ayen yeɛnan d wayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Lameɛna amdebbeṛ di tejmaɛt ur ilaq ara ad afen deg-s lɣaci wayen ara s-d-ssukksen, ilaq ad yesɛu yiwet n tikkelt kan, ad yili d win iḥekkmen deg iman-is, d asigna d aberkan ; ad yili d win yessexṛaben deg waman seg-s, d asigna d abeṛṛani.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yellan di leswaṛ n temdint n Tibeṛun, akk-d Tinyas yellan di leswaṛ n temdint n Qiṛwan, ama di tmurt n Tyatir, ama di tmurt n Maṣer, ama di lweqt i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer, ț-țilawin-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen iweɛṛen n wat Isṛail, win akken ur neqbil ara ad yerwi lɣellan di tmurt n Yahuda.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij-nni ayen ara sen-ifken d wayen yellan deg-s.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Heggit iman-nwen, ɛiwzet, beggset ɣef yiman-nwen tceɛlem tiftilin-nwen !
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus.
Imdanen n ddunit meṛṛa ad ilin di lfeṛḥ ameqqran imi mmuten. Ad țemceggaɛen tirezfin tirezfin-nsen, ur sɛint ara ayen ara ččen.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ.
Amdan daɣen ț-țideț, win i d-yusan s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i gellan si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad ilin d imqedsen, d wid yesɛan tazmert kan i gețmeslay akk-d Lmasiḥ.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass n lɛid n Tfaska, wa mkul ass i deg ara d-teḥyu si ger lmegtin. Ass n Tfaska ț-țunezduɣt n izimer n leslak, a d-yeǧǧ ad yeksen ṭṭlam i yiḍ di leɛyubat n Lmasiḥ.
Lɛeskeṛ melmi ara d-yekcem tamurt n Jlili armi d lweqt n usqiṛifa neɣ imi qṛib a d-yaweḍ waḍu ɣer lmeqṣud-nni,
M'ara yeččaṛ, iḥewwaten a t-id-jebden ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, dɣa ad qqimen iwakken ad fernen iselman, ad jemɛen wid yelhan, ad ḍeggṛen wid n diri iwakken ad țțaɣen awal ;
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
M'ara bdunt fessunt n uxerḍel n tigzirt, neɣ m'ulac qṛib a d-yaweḍ wass wis xemsin, sseɣṛet-itent deg yiḍ, axaṭer yewweḍ-ed wass n tafat.
Ass n lḥisab, tagellit n tmurt n Ḥabac ajenwi i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s, zzuɣṛen-ț lebḥuṛ ɣer lqaɛa, armi d ass i deg nesɛa usigna.
Di tmurt-nni, llan imeksawen ițnusun di lexlawi, țemyezwaǧen wway gar-asen ; aṭas ara d-ikecmen tamusni-nsen n tmes tețfeǧǧiǧ, ad ifṛeḥ aṭas.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant, uqbel ad iskkuɛ uyaziḍ, ad iyi-tnekkeṛ ula d nutni seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Beggnen-d s tikli-nsen belli ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, deg waṭas yid-sen aɛebbed i gura. Iqeddacen-nsen ț-țqeddacin n tejmaɛt i d-yețwaceggɛen d lweɛda i Sidi Ṛebbi s yisem n leqdic i Sidi Ṛebbi.
S wakka ihi, a nennadit ɣef wayen ara ɣ-d-yawin wayen yeɛnan leslak i ɣ-isnernin di liman, Ɛisa Lmasiḥ ur ilaq ara a d-nextiṛ ger wayen akk i sen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi.
lameɛna ilaq-as ad yaɣ awal i wid ițelhayen yid-es, iseddayen lecɣal-nsen, ɣuṛṛen-d wid s tmes, akk-d wid i t-yesseɣlin deg awal-nsen, waggur-nsen ur steɛfayen ara.
